Miscellaneous Information – Vivo (MNC 06)
IMSI Structure:
The IMSI complies with the GSM 03.03 and ITU-T E.212 and has a fixed length of 15 digits. It is composed as follows:
724 06 h1 h2 Z1 Z2 Z3 Z4 Z5 Z6 Z7 Z8 h1 = 0...9, h2 = 0...9, Z1...Z8 = 00000000...99999999
